{"tid":1737243,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黑警覺得大學係示威者「出擊據點」   港豬覺得大學係要放棄  一齊係街同黑警捉伊因","createTime":"2019-11-19T02:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T02:15:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"27ffeeba5977a2d89840cceb01a33f8582adb3ad","tid":1737243,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:02:53.000Z","msg":"黑警既戰術想法係：大學係易守難攻, 尤其是堅守既人已有雞尾酒及弓箭, 仲爆埋CHEM LAB<br />\n會係一個出擊據點, 控制附近地區<br />\n所以只能圍, 以及勸降, 強攻會有傷亡<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/399298/11-17-未來一哥鄧炳強再上陣-下午理大坐鎮-阻示威者出尖咀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F399298%2F11-17-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%A3-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%88%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%90%E9%8E%AE-%E9%98%BB%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%96%E5%92%80&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=57d75be5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/399298/11-17-未來一哥鄧炳強再上陣-下午理大坐鎮-阻示威者出尖咀</a><br />\n<br />\n【11.17】未來一哥鄧炳強再上陣 下午理大坐鎮 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">阻示威者出尖咀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3565929/org/8d43900eac67c42c3bb91b4b4a305f09.jpg/51xF9iyJGczi3H-vuCpEbb0pfZTXFdIYgTrEmYE6xJk?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3565929%2Forg%2F8d43900eac67c42c3bb91b4b4a305f09.jpg%2F51xF9iyJGczi3H-vuCpEbb0pfZTXFdIYgTrEmYE6xJk%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=1ff5f57c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大學據守, 真係被黑警係據點拉到既人, 十分之少<br />\n被拉得多既, 係逃走去街上, 以及投降既人<br />\n係街度同黑警捉伊因, 至今已被拉3000人+<br />\n<br />\n黑警最怕係, 越黎越多建築物被佔領<br />\n<br />\n據點儲糧不足<br />\n其他據點又唔出擊<br />\n都唔知想點...."},{"pid":"ddc1c920974f07f73f7563da537d2ec8c482c01d","tid":1737243,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:03:50.000Z","msg":"唔好拿2014年比啦<br />\n<br />\n2014年手無寸鐵, 又佔6條來回線馬路日曬雨淋<br />\n<br />\n人地WIN高既係點：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.rasset.ie/00086bd8-800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.rasset.ie%2F00086bd8-800.jpg&h=97c1f2c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76a27273437bf17d636fe750bbbc06528bc2cad9","tid":1737243,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:15:49.000Z","msg":"黑警最驚既係：<br />\nD示威者堅守咗係大學, 易守難攻<br />\n示威者係大學據點入面, 一直製造唔同既工具<br />\n<br />\n係街捉伊因, 示威者既工具及戰術係好缺乏, 基本上只能就地取材<br />\n<br />\n係據點入面, 就乜柒都有時間整到出嚟, 所以好撚驚<br />\n<br />\n點解無2016年既盾陣呢？因為今日示威者要係街跑嘛, 咪無法整囉<br />\n整唔到, 黑警咪可以瘋狂衝捉囉<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2016/02/15/a05a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2016%2F02%2F15%2Fa05a.jpg&h=c1b47b8f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}